Territory code list, and ISO-3166-2 sub-territory lists, and all their
translations in gettext .po form.

%lang_package

%prep
%setup -q -n %{name}-%{name}-%{version}

%build
%configure
%make_build

%install
%make_install
%find_lang iso_639 %{name}.lang
